snippet.title: v3.9 [Starlit Sanctum] Trailer - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Her lance sunders the darkness and illumines the sky. The knight descends when stardust converge!

HI3 v3.9 [Starlit Sanctum] coming soon! Durandal's S-rank battlesuit [Bright Knight: Excelsis] debuts, Story Chapter XVI [Imminent Storm] and spring event [Honkai Kingdoms: ZERO] await!

Subscribe our YouTube and turn on notification for latest video : http://bit.ly/HonkaiImpact3rdYTB
